00:47:01.860 --> 00:47:02.986
Hyeong-ju!

779
00:47:03.070 --> 00:47:05.781
Hyeong-ju. I'm sorry!

780
00:47:05.864 --> 00:47:07.449
Forgive me. Please?

781
00:47:07.533 --> 00:47:09.701
-Spare me!
-I'm sorry.

782
00:47:09.785 --> 00:47:12.371
-You've got to spare me.
-I'm fucking sorry!

783
00:47:12.454 --> 00:47:14.373
-Forgive us. or we're dead.
-It's okay.

784
00:47:14.456 --> 00:47:15.707
Honestly. it's okay.

785
00:47:16.208 --> 00:47:17.751
Don't do this. It's fine.

786
00:47:17.835 --> 00:47:20.337
No. please spare me. I'm really sorry.

787
00:47:27.469 --> 00:47:28.428
Hyeong-ju.

788
00:47:32.266 --> 00:47:33.600
Are you really okay?

789
00:47:57.958 --> 00:47:58.917
I'm sorry.

790
00:48:32.951 --> 00:48:34.870
If you don't want classes. don't come.

791
00:48:34.953 --> 00:48:37.581
If you don't want to study. then don't.
It's your life.

792
00:48:38.332 --> 00:48:39.166
Butâ€¦

793
00:48:42.002 --> 00:48:43.629
don't get in someone else's way.

794
00:48:46.048 --> 00:48:49.676
Don't assume your minute
is the same as another person's.

795
00:48:50.969 --> 00:48:52.512
It may feel the same nowâ€¦

796
00:48:58.477 --> 00:49:01.271
but later. it'll have made
decades of difference.

797
00:49:12.157 --> 00:49:13.200
Understood. you punks?

798
00:49:13.867 --> 00:49:14.701
Yes. sir!

799
00:49:15.702 --> 00:49:17.371
Why are you guys silent? Understood?

800
00:49:17.454 --> 00:49:18.580
Yes. sir!

801
00:49:33.470 --> 00:49:36.473
<i>I will report</i>
<i>on the results of the ERPB's work.</i>

802
00:49:37.307 --> 00:49:40.477
Through our inspector's efforts
at Guun High-Tech High School.

803
00:49:40.560 --> 00:49:43.897
the ERPB has resolved
violations of the right to learn.

804
00:49:43.981 --> 00:49:45.482
To prevent any recurrence.

805
00:49:45.565 --> 00:49:49.861
we will take the following actions
alongside related departments.

806
00:49:49.945 --> 00:49:50.779
TATTOO REMOVAL CLINIC

807
00:49:50.862 --> 00:49:54.241
<i>From now on.</i>
<i>tattoos will be banned in all schools.</i>

808
00:49:55.117 --> 00:49:57.285
If you move.
your bare skin will get burned.

809
00:49:58.495 --> 00:50:01.957
{\an8}<i>Motorcycles will be prohibited</i>
<i>on school grounds.</i>

810
00:50:02.457 --> 00:50:05.544
YOU'LL BE A GREAT MECHANIC
YOUR FRIEND. GEUN-DAE

811
00:50:11.299 --> 00:50:13.427
<i>Should a student join or attempt to join</i>

812
00:50:13.510 --> 00:50:17.514
<i>bullying gangs. school gangs.</i>
<i>or any organized crime groups.</i>

813
00:50:17.597 --> 00:50:19.307
<i>they will face adult charges</i>

814
00:50:19.391 --> 00:50:21.935
<i>and penalties under the law</i>
<i>on organized crime groups.</i>

815
00:50:22.686 --> 00:50:27.357
Finally. we will work
with the Ministry of Justice and the MSIT

816
00:50:27.441 --> 00:50:30.360
to continuously take action on
millennial and Gen Z gangs

817
00:50:30.444 --> 00:50:33.030
that recruit members through social media.

818
00:50:33.530 --> 00:50:35.407
<i>We at the ERPB</i>

819
00:50:35.991 --> 00:50:39.661
<i>will do our best to uphold</i>
<i>students' rights to compulsory education.</i>

820
00:50:39.745 --> 00:50:40.579
Turn off the TV!

821
00:50:40.662 --> 00:50:41.705
Yes. sir.

822
00:50:41.788 --> 00:50:43.457
Oh wow!

823
00:50:43.540 --> 00:50:46.084
You walked out of there.
and now you're here.

824
00:50:47.377 --> 00:50:50.714
Minister. don't you think
you're on TV too much lately?

825
00:50:50.797 --> 00:50:52.549
Why? Do you want to be on it?

826
00:50:52.632 --> 00:50:55.469
That's not what I meant.
You just seem to be enjoying it.

827
00:50:55.552 --> 00:50:56.803
Am I not allowed to?

828
00:50:56.887 --> 00:50:58.180
Of course you are.

829
00:50:58.263 --> 00:51:01.058
Did you see that?
"Those who disrupt learning. listen up."

830
00:51:01.141 --> 00:51:03.643
"Don't get in the way
of compulsory education." So cool.

831
00:51:04.978 --> 00:51:08.940
May I interrupt your conversation
for a brief moment?

832
00:51:09.024 --> 00:51:09.858
What is it?

833
00:51:09.941 --> 00:51:13.945
While carrying out my duties recently.
I incurred a few expenses.

834
00:51:14.029 --> 00:51:15.906
Yes. you should claim expenses.

835
00:51:15.989 --> 00:51:17.115
What are they?

836
00:51:17.616 --> 00:51:19.493
I was mugged

837
00:51:20.619 --> 00:51:22.329
about three times in total.

838
00:51:22.412 --> 00:51:23.955
Oh. mugged?

839
00:51:24.664 --> 00:51:26.458
They took 40.000 won in cash

840
00:51:26.541 --> 00:51:29.795
and 500 won for premium coffee
at a vending machine.

841
00:51:29.878 --> 00:51:31.797
And outside the workshop.

842
00:51:31.880 --> 00:51:35.884
a pair of sneakers worth about 125.000 won
called Nike Air Forceâ€¦

843
00:51:36.468 --> 00:51:39.596
Let's just say white Nike shoes
were taken from me.

844
00:51:39.679 --> 00:51:43.767
And I was microwaving
a 2.200-won Uiseong garlic sausage

845
00:51:43.850 --> 00:51:46.103
at the school snack bar.

846
00:51:46.186 --> 00:51:48.188
and that was taken too.

847
00:51:48.271 --> 00:51:51.775
So I ultimately spent 167.700 won

848
00:51:51.858 --> 00:51:53.944
from my personal funds.

849
00:51:54.027 --> 00:51:57.197
Would I be able to claim those?

850
00:51:57.781 --> 00:51:58.657
Sure.

851
00:51:59.407 --> 00:52:01.451
Was anything else taken?

852
00:52:01.535 --> 00:52:03.245
Wellâ€¦

853
00:52:03.745 --> 00:52:05.247
MEDICAL BILLSâ€¦

854
00:52:05.330 --> 00:52:06.832
No. nothing else.

855
00:52:08.041 --> 00:52:10.210
I see. Go ahead and claim the expenses.

856
00:52:10.794 --> 00:52:11.920
Thank you. sir.

857
00:52:15.924 --> 00:52:17.300
Should I buy you a sausage?

858
00:52:18.135 --> 00:52:20.345
Pardon? No. sir.

859
00:52:20.428 --> 00:52:23.682
-It's fine.
-Have one of those Uiseong garlic things.

860
00:52:23.765 --> 00:52:24.766
-Go on.
-Hey.

861
00:52:25.517 --> 00:52:26.351
He's just a kid.

862
00:52:26.434 --> 00:52:29.020
-But he said he had it taken--
-That's enough.

863
00:55:16.938 --> 00:55:19.899
